1772574209567052	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3hgs		item.create	bn-2syh	{"description":"Currently, punting a goal bone only removes the goal itself from bn next candidates. Its child and dependent bones remain fully eligible. The desired behavior is that punting a goal should also suppress all descendants — none of them should appear in triage or next recommendations. Fix: extend propagate_parent_blocked() in triage_support.rs to treat a punted ancestor the same as a blocked one, propagating a blocker count to all descendants when any ancestor has urgency == Punt.","kind":"task","title":"Punted goal bones should suppress children in triage/next"}	blake3:gpewbJQahTfRS06ZVuqbxz8Y8b9-UM-V9WlJgwop6SM
